codefresh:index/accountAdmins:AccountAdm.description:
## # Account Admins resource

Use this resource to set a list of admins for any account.

{{% examples %}}
## Example Usage
{{% example %}}
### Example 2

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as codefresh from "@pierskarsenbarg/codefresh";
import * as codefresh from "@pulumi/codefresh";

const testAccount = new codefresh.Account("testAccount", {
    limits: [{
        collaborators: 25,
        dataRetentionWeeks: 5,
    }],
    builds: [{
        parallel: 2,
    }],
});
const admin = codefresh.getUser({
    email: "<EXISTING USER EMAIL>",
});
const testAccountAdmins = new codefresh.AccountAdmins("testAccountAdmins", {
    accountId: testAccount.id,
    users: [admin.then(admin => admin.userId)],
});
```
```python
